In the end, Max realized that having a little buddy to take care of wasn't so bad after all. Sure, the puppy was a handful, but he made life more exciting and gave Max a reason to get up in the morning (besides breakfast, of course). And if there was one thing that Max knew for sure, it was that a life without a little bit of chaos and mischief just wasn't worth living.

