4. Chicken - when our undefeated teammate Gertrude puts on her game face and gets ready to viciously return the meatball, her opponent will be too "chicken" to hit it back.
5. Lamb - when you see a spike opportunity with that meatball, score the point and then yell out "Wham lamb, thank you, ma'am!"

If you have any questions about how these meatballs should be served, then please don't hesitate to contact me. Personally, I think they should be served with a breadstick and a chilled glass of red wine!

Regards,

Your Captain

