Used to do it as a side business, but my job changed and now just sell kids books because I love books (include that I am an English teacher and have a 6 year old who reads a lot) and think that reading is important for kids and books should be more accessible. I buy them cheap and keep prices cheap ($3-10, average $5). All books are in good condition, some new. Teacher discount of 20%. It should be 200-300 words (preferably closer to 250).
